13 CHAPTER 70. CLICK-TO-CANCEL ACT
14 §3301. Short title
15 This Chapter shall be known and may be cited as the "Click-to-Cancel Act".
16 §3302. Definitions
17 In this Chapter, unless the context clearly indicates otherwise, the following
18 terms have the following definitions:
19 (1) "Automatic renewal contract" means a plan or arrangement in which a
20 paid subscription or purchasing agreement commitment for goods or services is
